      "releaseNotes": "- Adds the \"Note Values\" customization to all staff-based exercises. This feature allows exercises to display quarter and half notes in addition to whole notes.\n- Fixes an issue where audio might not play after watching a video in another app. If you encounter audio issues in this version, please contact us so we can further diagnose.\n- Fixes various graphical glitches and layout issues when running on newer devices.",
